Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然發生這種奇蹟?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到這裡的話應該沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我受死吧
